[http://www.shimizu.com.hk/Support/Wlan/NWH660.htm Downloads on ''shimizu.com.hk''] :There would appear to be multiple HW revisions of this device. This device does not appear to have a Web configuration interface. The FCC test report states the device uses a reverse SMA connector. However, it is not clear if this means reverse polarity SMA or reverse threaded SMA. "68-806900-06 REV:A2" is silkscreened on the wireless module. The default SSID may be '''Wireless'''.
